# products

<div>

[Airlight](https://airlight.pro)
- Easiest way to access make your favourite web apps like ChatGPT, Perplexity, etc accessible using a shortcut like spotlight search. (available to download)

[Quick Search](https://github.com/nidhishgajjar/quicksearch-api)
- A conversational search engine. Quickest way to find accurate information. (obsolete)

[Phone AI](https://phoneaiagent.com)
- Phone AI agent to handle business phone calls autonomously. [interviewed at Y Combinator](https://www.ycombinator.com) (obsolete)

Maven
- AI-powered deal-sourcing agent for private equity firms. Tell Maven what you are looking for in natural language and it'll scour the web and use tools like Google Maps to find hidden M&A gems. (obsolete)

[Scigic](https://scigic.com)
- Browser Reimagined - automanaged tabs, AI auto-delegates query to perplexity or google, smart vertical tab switcher, and more. (obsolete)


</div>

